{"block1":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The <a href=\"http:\/\/www.evaidyaji.com\/Ayurveda\/Ayurvedic_Supplements_for_Gout\"  >Ayurvedic Medicine kit<\/a> for gout contains Gout Ayur capsules, Detox herbal tea and Kaishore Guggulu. Gout Ayur capsules provide nourishment to the joints affected by gout, and improve the functioning of muscles and joints. Detox herbal tea flushes toxins like uric acid out of the body and prevents their deposits. Kaishore Guggulu is a supplement that supports metabolism and reduces production of uric acid.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ingredients<\/h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gout Ayur capsules<\/strong><\/p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gorakhmundi (Sphaeranthus indicus) &ndash; controls uric acid levels<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Guduchi (Tinospora cordifolia) &ndash; enhances immunity<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Manjishtha &ndash; diuretic<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shunthi (Zinziber officinale) &ndash; reduces pain<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shallaki (Boswellia Serrata) &ndash; anti-inflammatory, reduces joint swelling and pain, and generally improves joint health<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ashwagandha &ndash; improves immunity, has been shown to be helpful in arthritis and gout<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ajwain (Trachyspermum ammi) &ndash; flushes out uric acid from the body<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; <strong>Detox Herbal tea<\/strong><\/p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pippali (Piper longum) &ndash; increases the liver&rsquo;s ability to remove toxins from the body<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dalchini (Cinnamon) &ndash; keeps liver healthy<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Amalaki (Indian gooseberry) &ndash; rich in vitamin C, high in anti-oxidants, also increases immunity<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Haritaki (Terminalia chebula) &ndash; increases immune function<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Haridra (Turmeric) &ndash; increases immunity, relieves inflammation and pain, also reduces uric acid deposits<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maricha (Piper nigrum) &ndash; relieves pain, stimulates the digestive and excretory system<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Manjishtha<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp;Kaishore Guggulu<\/strong><\/p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Guduchi<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Haritaki<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bibhitaki (Terminalia bellirica) &ndash; helpful in removing toxins<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Amalaki<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nishotha (Operculina turpethum) &ndash; enhances metabolism, keeps liver healthy, expels unwanted fluid from the body, also a good antioxidant<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vidanga (Embelia ribes) &ndash; keeps digestive tract healthy<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Guggulu &ndash; detoxifies blood, prevents inflammation and gout<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dosage<\/h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Recommended dosage of Gout Ayur and Kaishore Guggulu is 2 capsules\/tablets each twice a day with hot water. 2 cups of detox herbal tea should also be consumed each day.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Price<\/h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">1-month supply of the Ayurvedic medicine kit costs $35.95, and a 10% discount is available when ordering a 3-month supply.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Guarantee<\/h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">There is no money-back guarantee, but the products are made of all-natural products and do not contain any chemicals. They are manufactured in accordance with Good Manufacturing Practices prescribed by FDA.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Overall Value<\/h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">While this is a good product containing herbal components, it is quite&nbsp;costly compared to substitute gout treatments like GoutClear that have been proven to be effective and are backed by 100% guarantees offered by their companies. This ayurvedic medicine seems to have an overall benefit in treating gout, but it does not come with any guarantee. However, herbal remedies usually do not have any side effects and have been used in Indian medicine for hundreds of years.<\/p>\r\n"}